{
  "texts": [
    "Our analysis revealed that none of the evaluated approaches consistently achieved high detection rates for ChatGPT-generated text.",
    "The most effective online tool we examined demonstrated a success rate of less than 50%, as depicted in Table I.",
    "Notably, the maximum accuracy achieved by the detector was around 47%.",
    "In addition, recently the authors of [34] propose a ChatGPT-detector, CheckGPT, tailored specifically for academic abstracts of research papers, achieving in this domain an accuracy of 98% to 99%.",
    "Nevertheless, their detector's performance significantly declined, as we evaluated it against our benchmark dataset."
  ]
}